---
title: Thai-Inspired Black Beans with Fried Eggs and Garlic Rice
description: A stellar vegetarian spin on beloved Thai dish pad krapow is on the table tonight. Black beans and crunchy veggies are cooked in an umami-rich sauce, then spooned over savoury garlic rice. When you break a runny yolk of fried egg over everything, you'll finally know food bliss!
